1. open in broswer 다운
2. new text file - 확장자 명 .html - ! 엔터
3. 자동으로 뜬다.

이때 

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Document</title>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>Hello</h1> //body부분은 우리가 작성해줘야함.
</body>
</html>




